➜卫健委、教育部：开学前进行连续14天每日体温测量
http://www.sohu.com/a/412994717_114986	46061
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
showVrsPlayer({
bid:'209765436',
width: '500',
height: '375',
autoplay: false,
